vice\n4. **无Node级问题**：虽然有两个节点内存可用性下降，但变化率相对较小（23-48%）\n\n**假设验证结论：**\n- **支持**emailservice是根因的假设，因为：\n  - emailservice的延迟增长是最显著的（196%+）\n  - 下游服务（checkoutservice、frontend）的延迟增长模式符合上游故障传播\n  - 没有发现更底层的Node或DB级问题\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"pod_processes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"io_util\", \"memory_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标出现极端恶化（增长196%+），从正常5-6秒延迟暴增至67-68万毫秒\",\n      \"evidence\": \"emailservice-0: rrt_max从5831ms增至675341ms(196.58%)，emailservice-1: rrt_max从5167ms增至678022ms(196.97%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标受上游emailservice影响而恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从220289ms增至2147140ms(162.78%)，rrt从6685ms增至80658ms(169.38%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标受下游服务链影响而恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: rrt_max从213344ms增至2053968ms(162.36%)，frontend-1: rrt_max从266754ms增至2153091ms(155.91%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
